  _characterSheet: {fileID: 0}
  _missions:
  - Act: 2
    QuestId: caldenWarning
    Title: Father Calden's Doubt
    Summary: Warn Wren away from the deeper wood and close the chapel garden.
  - Act: 3
    QuestId: caldenReconcile
    Title: The Chapel Garden Opens
    Summary: Read the old records and return the garden key.
  _quotes:
  - Text: The edge of a thing is not the thing.
    Context: Warning Wren about the deeper wood.
  - Text: Being late to wisdom. Being early to harm.
    Context: Naming what he fears.
  - Text: Because it was useful to people who were not powerful.
    Context: Explaining why the old knowledge was buried.
